cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper heavily relies on deep learning based detectors to annotate objects/tags from images. 
2) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a Genetic Algorithm based method to generate an optimal banner layout. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training and evaluating multiple models for ranking the generated banners. 
4) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a potential category as the paper discusses the importance of homepage banners in optimizing click through rates and improving personalization. 
5) cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating and ranking visual content for e-commerce websites.
